<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Turtle Shelter Project</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        /* Transparent Navigation Bar (Static at Top-Right) */
        .nav-bar {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            height: 50px;
        }

        .nav-bar a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-bar a:hover {
            color: lightgreen;
        }

        /* Header Section with Full-Height Image */
        .header-section {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: calc(50vh + 50px);
            margin-top: -50px;
            background: url('/assets/sea-turtle-under-3440x1440-12941.jpg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header-section h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .header-section p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .header-section .volunteer-btn {
            background-color: lightgreen;
            color: black;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .header-section .volunteer-btn:hover {
            background-color: #89e589;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            width: 100%; /* Full width */
            margin: 0; /* Remove extra margins */
            padding: 20px 0; /* Add padding for spacing */
            background-color: #343a40; /* Dark background for footer */
            color: white; /* Text color */
            text-align: center; /* Center align text */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Transparent Navigation Bar -->
    <div class="nav-bar">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/jenstory">Jen's Story</a>
        <a href="/eventRequest">Request Event</a>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
        
        
    </div>

    <!-- Header Section with Image and Centered Button -->
    <div class="header-section">
        <h1>Welcome to the Turtle Shelter Project</h1>
        <p>Providing solutions for homelessness during extreme weather.</p>
        <a href="/newvolunteer" class="volunteer-btn">Become a Volunteer</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="content">
      <!-- Section 1: About the Turtle Shelter Project -->
      <section class="mt-5">
          <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-4">About the Turtle Shelter Project</h2>
          <div style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
              <p class="text-center">
                  Every year, as temperatures drop, countless individuals experiencing homelessness face life-threatening challenges. 
                  Without access to proper shelter, conditions like hypothermia and frostbite become imminent dangers.
              </p>
              <p class="text-center">
                  Rural areas are particularly vulnerable, as shelters in these regions often lack the capacity and resources to handle 
                  the increased demand caused by harsh weather. This creates a critical need for solutions that go beyond traditional methods.
              </p>
              <p class="text-center">
                  The Turtle Shelter Project was born out of this necessity. By using advanced foam clothing technology, we’ve developed 
                  portable vests that provide warmth and protection. These vests are uniquely designed to retain body heat—even in wet conditions—ensuring that everyone, regardless of their circumstances, has a chance to stay warm and safe.
              </p>
          </div>
      </section>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
        <img src="/assets/TransparentTSPLogo.png" alt="Description of Image" style="width: 200px; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;">
    </div>
      
      <!-- Section 2: Our Mission -->
      <section class="mt-5">
          <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <div style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
              <p class="text-center">
                  At the Turtle Shelter Project, our mission is simple yet profound: to save lives and restore dignity. 
                  We believe that everyone deserves warmth, safety, and the chance to survive—even in the most challenging conditions.
              </p>
              <p class="text-center">
                  By combining innovative technology with community-driven support, we aim to bridge the gap between homelessness 
                  and hope. Our foam vests are more than just clothing—they’re a symbol of resilience and care, a tangible way 
                  to show that no one is forgotten.
              </p>
              <p class="text-center" style="padding-bottom:30px;">
                  Together, we can create a future where no one is left vulnerable to the cold, and everyone has access to life-saving solutions during the harshest winters.
              </p>
          </div>
      </section>
  </main>
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; padding-bottom:20px;">
    <img src="/assets/cover.png" alt="Description of Image" style="width: 900px; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;">
</div>
  
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Turtle Shelter Project. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="/privacy" style="color: white; text-decoration: none;">Privacy Policy</a> |
            <a href="/terms" style="color: white; text-decoration: none;">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
